Bootstrap: localimage
From: ./ubuntu_22.04.sif

%post
    set -e

    # Install Python and pytest
    apt-get update
    apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends python3 python3-pip
    pip3 install --no-cache-dir pytest

    # Create required directory hierarchy
    mkdir -p /home/user/builds/logs
    mkdir -p /home/user/builds/reports

    # Populate the Maven build log with the exact expected contents
    cat > /home/user/builds/logs/build_2023-08-15.log <<'EOF'
[INFO] Uploaded: commons-io-2.11.0.jar
[INFO] Uploaded: guava-32.1.0.jar
[ERROR] FAILED to upload: junit-4.13.2.jar
[ERROR] FAILED to upload: log4j-1.2.17.jar
[INFO] Uploaded: slf4j-api-1.7.36.jar
EOF

    # Set permissions: reports directory must be writable by the non-root user
    chmod 0777 /home/user/builds/reports
    chmod 0755 /home/user/builds/logs
    chmod 0644 /home/user/builds/logs/build_2023-08-15.log

%labels
    chmod 755 /home/user

    Author Maven-Log-Exercise
    Description "Environment for generating Maven upload-status summaries"

%help
    This container provides the prerequisites for the Maven upload-status summary
    exercise. It includes:
      • Pre-created build log at /home/user/builds/logs/build_2023-08-15.log
      • Writable reports directory at /home/user/builds/reports
      • Python 3 and pytest for automated evaluation